      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/korriku/{size}/18544_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-02-10T22:05:43.352Z",
      "cooked": "<p>modesti Simone Cristicchi me thellesine dhe ndjeshmerine ‘Abi cura di me’ - nje ndjekes i tradites me te mire i kenges italiane - me Claudio Baglionin perfaqesues te kesaj tradite- vendi 5te, mund te ishte i 2-3 vende me lart pa konkurencen nga te rinjte qe zune keto vende.</p>\n<p>Mahmood e vendosi fatin me zerin special, me ritmin dhe pasurine e melodise se tij, ‘Soldi’ ishte nje rryme e fresket oksigjeni.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/10cb15a579b6c85bd0e53db220703a161a5b078e.png\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/10cb15a579b6c85bd0e53db220703a161a5b078e\" title=\"sanremo 1.PNG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/10cb15a579b6c85bd0e53db220703a161a5b078e.png\" alt=\"sanremo%201\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/10cb15a579b6c85bd0e53db220703a161a5b078e_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">sanremo 1.PNG</span><span class=\"informations\">926×729 35.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div><br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1c317c5ed4bda7b2d3a55573707c4d83d70f91bd.jpeg\" alt=\"sanremo%202\" width=\"626\" height=\"164\"></p>",
